{"tid":2394030,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"SCP-4001 全人類檔案庫 永恆之亞歷山大城 Alexandria Eternal","createTime":"2021-02-04T01:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T01:46:12.000Z","uid":129010,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"162efc3a1ce4d9f80b74506c02f9c72ff0838804","tid":2394030,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"SCP-4001 是一個檔案庫，內有迄今為止全部人類的完整檔案，且持續更新中。每個曾經存在過的人類在此檔案庫內都有一本對應書籍，詳細記載其人生中的所有重大事件。書本內容代表了其對應人員的歷史。改動書本內容會對現實即時產生相應的影響⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n// SCP基金會是一個虛構的組織，負責搜尋並收容各種具有異常物體。版權 CC-BY-SA。<br />\nWiki <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/SCP基金會\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2FSCP%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%9C%83&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=765f8185\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/SCP基金會</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTube影片<br />\n長約15分鐘，CC字幕提供<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yoMxJhEQ2cM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyoMxJhEQ2cM&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=788782c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yoMxJhEQ2cM</a><br />\n<br />\n影片截圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pj31gfw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPj31gfw.jpg&h=769dccbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqGFwOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtqGFwOR.jpg&h=b9a406d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNMFwOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNMFwOR.jpg&h=a42db7cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q40i2Vw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq40i2Vw.jpg&h=11750d9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c9fa735f736968471a38af23ffeffb1f415596c","tid":2394030,"uid":27597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img s